                                <H2>'Transport Reforms? Yes, it' time for change!'</H2>
                                
                         <p><div class="textblock">
                       
                    
               
                    
                 <img src="../images/43184.jpg" width="705" height="1147" border="0" title="Prof. Amal Kumarage,Head, Department of Transport and Logistics Management" />
                      <BR />

                        </p><div align="right" class="style10">
                                 <A href="https://www.ceylontoday.lk/22-84226-news-detail-transport-reforms-yes-its-time-for-change.html" target="_blank"><b><em>Read more</em></b></A></div>
                       
