<h1>Press News Releases</h1>
<p>Being comprised of the academic pionners of the transport and logistics sector, the Dept. of TLM appears in the public press. Here are some of the newspaper aricles: </p><br />
               
                  <table>
					<tr height="30px">
						<th width="160" class="first"><strong>Date</strong></th>
						<th width="505"><strong>Title</strong></th>					
					</tr>
                    
                    <tr class="row-b">
						<td class="first">Sunday, 23<sup>rd</sup> August 2015 @ The Sunday Times  </td>
						<td><a href="http://www.sundaytimes.lk/150823/sunday-times-2/wanted-a-new-leadership-culture-for-public-bodies-161577.html">Wanted:' A new leadership culture for public bodies '</a></td>
						
					</tr> 
                    
